Description:
  Creates a new basic front-end web application.

Options:
  Task runner: Use Gulp or Grunt
  Sass: Include Sass (using libsass)
  Bootstrap: Include Bootstrap or Bootstrap Sass if Sass is included
  Modernizr: Include Modernizr

Example:
  yo webapp

  This will create:
    Depending on the task runner you choose:
      gulpfile.babel.js: Configuration for the Gulp task runner.
      Gruntfile.js: Configuration for the Grunt task runner
    bower.json: Front-end packages installed by bower.
    package.json: Development packages installed by npm.

    app/: Your application files.
    test/: Unit tests for your application.
